Changelog
---------

0.2 (2017-07-09)
++++++++++++++++

**Bugfixes**

- Fix an error in the packaging that caused ``mackerel init`` command to fail
  due to the lack of ``config.ini``.

**Improvements**

- Rework the ``setup.py`` script to increase release automation.

0.1 (2017-07-09)
++++++++++++++++

* First preview release.


